but only on my butt,

04:41.583 --> 04:43.049
like it were a tail.

04:43.051 --> 04:45.451
A tail tie.

04:45.453 --> 04:47.586
Furguson, you have a knot!

04:47.588 --> 04:49.287
That salt water in here?

04:49.289 --> 04:51.222
You been hanging
down at the wharf again?

04:51.224 --> 04:52.890
Guess what.

04:52.892 --> 04:55.425
I took a chance with that
guy Fred, and I'm in love.

04:55.427 --> 04:56.459
That's incredible.

04:56.461 --> 04:58.427
