Hmm?

05:38.059 --> 05:40.225
Errands and a smoothie.

05:41.261 --> 05:42.693
Okay, everyone,
listen up.

05:44.630 --> 05:46.429
Here are your
new uniforms.

05:46.431 --> 05:48.464
