10:51.523 --> 10:52.855
(sighs)

10:52.857 --> 10:55.557
Uh, wow, I, um...

10:55.559 --> 10:57.859
I don't know
where I stand with my girl,

10:57.861 --> 11:00.695
and I can't talk to her,
because I am ashamed.

11:00.697 --> 11:01.862
Aw... Did he just
say "ashamed"?

11:01.864 --> 11:03.563
