Ashamed...

11:03.565 --> 11:05.531
of being beautiful?
Of being a man?

11:05.533 --> 11:07.499
Of being passionate?

11:07.501 --> 11:09.868
Ha! Then I'm ashamed, too.

11:09.870 --> 11:11.502
I say to you...

11:11.504 --> 11:12.736
let her in.

11:12.738 --> 11:13.570
(quietly):
Yes.

11:13.572 --> 11:15.138
All together now.

11:15.140 --> 11:17.907
